svg.text: In pairs, form a question-and-answer about what Little Wang wants to do next week based on the
following calendar. [See also Grammar 2, Lesson 6.] Insert
小王下个星期一要做什么？
Xiǎo Wáng xià ge xīngqīyī yào zuò shénme?
小王下个星期一要去上课。
Xiǎo Wáng xià ge xīngqīyī yào qù shàng kè.
Then discuss your partner’s plans for next week, e.g.:
你呢？你下个星期要做什么？
Nǐ ne? Nǐ xià ge xīngqī yào zuò shénme?
我下个星期一…… 星期二……
